title: The Library
description:
My computer was recently stolen and It was such a pain to rebuild my old archive... so I am putting the whole archive up as one big Mac torrent! Hopefully nobody will think I'm too retarded... but this will just make my life easier... I hope. I'm still rebuilding the archive so don't get upset if it looks incomplete. Also, since I'm a damn hippie ;) I seed from where ever I happen to be - some days I may only be able to up at 10k and someday a LOT faster... bare with me. Once there are more seeds everything will be a lot easier! I'll update each month with the new torrent overlapping the old one so there isn't unnecessary downloading. And obviously, only download what you want - some of this stuff is easily downloadable off the internet... it's just part of my archive so it's just here :)

I know I'm missing a lot still... 

Mulitple versions of the same thing are most likely because I only have a serial for the older one.

The collection should be relatively complete and up to date next month... hope you like it
